title: Cyphoma sedlaki
text:
Cyphoma sedlaki is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Ovulidae">Ovulidae</a>, the ovulids, cowry allies or false cowries.
Description.
The maximum recorded <a href="gastropod%20shell">shell</a> length is 26.9 mm.
Habitat.
It has been recorded at depths of 1.5 m.
